    <item>
      <title>随着危机加深，泰晤士水务债务保险公司聘请顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/thames-water-debt-insurer-taps-advisers-as-crisis-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，一家在泰晤士水务公用事业金融公司 (Thames Water Utilities Finance Plc) 持有至少 20 亿美元资金的美国保险公司正在与债券持有人和顾问合作，以在潜在的债务谈判之前保护他们的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/thames-water-debt-insurer-taps-advisers-as-crisis-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:36:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
